history.content:
Hey everyone! Wanted to share this opportunity here in case anyone is interested in exploring investment banking or finance in general!


From beginning in the Financial Sponsors Group of Morgan Stanley to now working as a Managing Director at DBO Partners, Madeleine McCarthy (Cal class of 2009) has seen many sides of investment banking in her illustrious career.

Join us on Friday (July 31st) at 4pm PT as Madeleine takes us through her journey from Cal to helping lead DBO Partners, and shares advice on how you too can build a successful career in finance.

Register here: https://zoom.us/meeting/register/tJMtcO2urDsoGdFsQLriFx7RSjlGbghF_c7m

This talk is part of Florian's weekly event series. Florian is a community of Cal alumni helping students pay for school without loans and get ahead in their careers. You can learn more at joinflorian.com.
history.subject: Building a Successful Career in Investment Banking
